metadata.name: PAIN DOES NOT WANT A CHILD
metadata.description:
I am not sick, I am not crazy.
 Maybe I'm a little different..!
 I don't want to have a child...!
A child who suffers and lives like me, suffers and laughs and goes on...!
 I sold my brain to survive...!
I myself am the meaning of suffering...!


pain does not want a child...!
